  <summary date="2019-10-23T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Susan Harwood Training Grant Program Authorization Act

This bill establishes a Susan Harwood Training Grant Program. Under the program, the Department of Labor must award grants to (1) provide&#160;training and education programs for employers and workers on the recognition, avoidance, and prevention of safety and health hazards in workplaces; and&#160;(2)&#160;inform workers of their rights and employers of their responsibilities under requirements governing occupational safety and health.</summary>
